        "en": "――A Few Hours Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "お、来た来た。家出娘を連れ戻しに来る奴らって\n本当に黒スーツなんだね～。どこのB級映画だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ here they come. The people who come to take their runaway daughter\nback really do wear black suits~. What is this‚ a B-movie?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.6333334565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "くくく、kana達を探してる探してる\n隠し撮りされてるなんて、まるで気付いてないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kukuku‚ they’re looking for us‚ looking for us.\nThey have no idea they’re being filmed secretly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、女の子が隠し撮りしながらはしゃいでますけど\nなんて言ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ that girl is happily filming everything in secret…\nWhat is she saying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.9000001232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "「凄い、配信の視聴者数がぐんぐん上がってるよ」\n「やっぱ、kanaちゃんって天才だね！」……だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Wow‚ the number of viewers on my stream is skyrocketing!”\n“kana-chan‚ you’re a genius‚ as expected!” …she said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、ネットでは話題になりますよね\nセレブの家の子供が、家出の実況配信をするなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’ll definitely make headlines online.\nA kid from a celebrity family livestreaming her own runaway…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.2000001232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ？\nいやー、kanaってばやっぱ頭いい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right?\nMan~‚ kana is so smart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……でも真相を知ったら、あの子は怒るでしょうねぇ\nせっかくの家出なのに、親も承知済みとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But she would be angry if she found out the truth.\nShe went to all the trouble of running away‚ but her parents knew about it all along…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5592108369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "いい？　{user}\n今からkanaの言う通りにしろよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ {user}.\nDo exactly as I say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3333382885
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あいつの家に、あんたから連絡を入れて\nお宅のお嬢さんが見つかりましたよってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Call her parents and tell them\nthat you’ve found their daughter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4666714986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、素直に連れ戻されてくれますかね？\n今までも家出を繰り返してるみたいですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But do you think she’ll go back with them without a fuss?\nIt seems she’s run away from home multiple times already…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.700004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.7333382885
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、無理でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ probably not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7333382885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "でも連れ戻さなくても、子供の居場所と無事が分かれば\n親はひとまず安心するでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even if they can’t bring her back‚ at least her parents will feel relieved\nknowing where she is and that she’s safe‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0666714986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.699994274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、自分から居場所を発信させればいいのよ\nバズりたいなら喜んでやるだろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So she just needs to broadcast her location herself.\nShe’ll be happy to do it if she wants to go viral.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ父親も、撮影協力してくれるのはいいけど\n黒スーツまで寄越してくるとは思わなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m glad the father agreed to help with the filming‚\nbut I didn’t expect him to send men in black suits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "エキストラ出演、お疲れさ～ん\nって何{user}。なんか言いたそうじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work on your extra role~!\nWhat’s wrong‚ {user}? You look like you want to say something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3666725158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.7666619579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……まぁ……\nこれは、丸く収まった、って言えるんでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… Well…\nIs it really okay to call this… a good outcome…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.0666619579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あいつは家出して、親から離れればひとまず満足\n父親は居場所が分かれば安心",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s satisfied just by running away from home and getting away from her parents‚\nand her father’s relieved if he knows where she is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "あの父親、kana達が日本からショーの仕事で来た\nって言ったら、宣伝に協力してくれるって言うし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told her father we were here from Japan for a show‚\nhe said he’d help us with promotion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.0333286245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "ラスベガスのホテルのオーナーも知り合いにいるから\n告知出してくれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And he knows the owner of a hotel in Las Vegas‚\nso he’s going to advertise us there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、持つべきはセレブとのコネだね～\nまさに、win-winって訳よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Man‚ it’s great to have connections with celebrities!\nIt’s a total win-win situation!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.9666619579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに、何事もなく収まった感じはしますけど\nkanaさんは、他に思うところがある気がして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right‚ it seems like everything worked out well‚\nbut I feel like you have something else on your mind‚ kana-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.7999952912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "……は？\n別に、そんなんある訳ないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nThere’s no way I do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、宣伝の効果もあって）\n（スリクスのライブは満員御礼となった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Later‚ thanks to the promotion‚）\n（ⅢX’s live was a sold-out success.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（これにはプロモーターも大喜びで、帰国前にもう一度）\n（より大きなステージに出してくれたのだった）",
      "translations": {
